<h3>Parking</h3>
<p>Parking at the hospital is on a barrier pay-on-exit scheme. The payment machines take cash, notes and credit cards. <br/>The charges are as follows:<br/>0-2 hours: £2<br/>2-3 hours: £3<br/>3-4 hours: £4<br/>4-8 hours: £6<br/>All day (24hours): £10<br/>All week (7 days): £20</p>
